    "It is unclear for which pathogens data availability would currently be a significant bottleneck.",
    "The increasing rate of generation of metagenomic data and its availability to tool developers may contribute to filling gaps in data for concerning pathogens, whether or not they are targeted.",
    "For more basic research, lack of negative data on host-pathogen protein interactions may be a limiting factor for some narrower use cases.",
    "128 Ongoing progress in high-throughput protein-protein interaction testing and single-cell proteomics is likely to contribute to suitable training data assets.",
